For some reason he wants my data and money but I don’t know him. You see my mom just have all my money to a Nigerian Prince who was trapped and needed help. She was good friends with him but she never heard back after he reclaimed his throne and he’s a poser who forgot who helped him. This app is just like that Prince he’ll take your money and information then ghost you. So lame but I guess I’m used to it by now. Since then my phone is covered in Cheeto dust and laggy AF.
literally took 69 years to download, is just a big waste of space honestly. wouldn’t recommend 😡
